name: the way
description: Taken in 2007 at Drinkeria Maldita, R. Voluntários da Pátria, 10 - Botafogo, Rio de Janeiro. This pub was opened in 2006 and is credited (alongside another bar called "Rosa de Ouro") with revitalizing the "Baixo Botafogo" region in Rio de Janeiro during the late 00s. In 2007, Drinkeria Maldita and Rosa de Ouro were the only two establishments in a region where more than 30 bars are located today. It closed a few years into the 2010s. Shot with Fuji Superia 1600. /// by KPLLO
